{"tid":2247259,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"護士的工作不等於照顧","createTime":"2020-10-17T16:37:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-19T11:58:59.000Z","uid":342891,"like":6,"dislike":41,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"7ad5080232798d5ce9dddd9b02b6eb924d5c5080","tid":2247259,"uid":342891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T16:37:50.000Z","msg":"這是香港人普遍的誤解，也是很多香港護士院校因為自己無能而希望洗學生和社會腦的方向，也是圖永續無理壟斷的醫生濫用公權力洗公眾腦的結果。<br />\n<br />\n在國際定義上護士是治療的決策者，現在在香港是有實無名，這必須要在法律上完全實現。外國護士法定獨立診療處方早己存在多年，而且行之有效，大量研究証實護士診治疾病臨床效果至少等於，很多時甚至優於醫生，包括死亡率更低。"},{"pid":"2aaea36b85146370b1a687b4b371244b11ece732","tid":2247259,"uid":57237,"like":11,"dislike":3,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T03:20:42.000Z","msg":"低賤的護士<br />\n有冇人考到醫科會唔讀走去讀護理？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00878931f1106f9162f45b6ebac6db43ceafdee7","tid":2247259,"uid":248054,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T04:30:03.000Z","msg":"咪就係<br />\n護士高級過醫生/治療師<br />\n醫生/治療師技術成分邊有護士咁高<br />\n醫生/治療師只不過係護士下屬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb67b51e233f4df9b55c27ee293708582471bbf8","tid":2247259,"uid":107269,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T04:43:38.000Z","msg":"本身想講你講d 野咁似facebook <br />\n小 wound nurse &amp; nursing tribe<br />\n條怨婦<br />\n<br />\n點知一 search, 原來真係"},{"pid":"b15024435ec90a59a47c0ea506859e2818d35f17","tid":2247259,"uid":228894,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T04:46:37.000Z","msg":"護士係肉便器"},{"pid":"d0cd55eafa34ca554fe5e518dff0343cc1c815da","tid":2247259,"uid":123456,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T04:47:46.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">想男護士用口幫我治療精液過量的病情<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"8fadbc1eb7062a2554864c573e1cad